Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙说这里是香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是未来的一种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许 那个假面人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这之后准备怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾越来越浓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样在这里停留的话也许很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 什么都看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不走散 不要放开手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是白色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 前面完全看不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用眼睛看到的东西在这里是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界全都是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里对你们来说是个不确定存在的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时空是和拉库利玛平行的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你们的角度来看 也是未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可能性之一的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这个世界是幻影的话 佑、鸦不都在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们两人在这里 所以我也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 制作好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢君 这个是表示时空构造的模型？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是内田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是连接总和了存在和被确定的无限延伸的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将其 实时印象化的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是意识的时空间的坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然以这里的系统的演算能力 只能制作出简易版
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样至少能知道遥是否存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要输入遥的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 遥还存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是在香格里拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是内田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是黛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黛博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从佐佐木教授那里听到了你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士你现在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在同一个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能和你见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想和你交谈的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田 你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去黛博士所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像能看见什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给人感觉很不好的城市啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市也不是实体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说那种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心啊 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是动摇之城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动摇你的心、你的回忆的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要迷失了你所期望的未来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间也有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁住的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的话应该没有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那里休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连床都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强啊 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 快去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该休息的时候就休息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然移动到那里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要开始了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在暖机中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黛博士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是内田小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和传闻一样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我读过了你的关于量子势能临界机的论文
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常有趣的猜想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 应该停止Magic Circle计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.43,0:09:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Circle计划里发现的大量θ素粒子如果连接了量子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发生强烈爆炸的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说 那也要发生了临界才可能的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你看一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里面 有这片地域的量子势能的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指明了这片地域正处于由量子引发的歪曲中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在这里发生了临界现象的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发生时空间的接触干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全时空、整个宇宙都可能就这么被消灭掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片地域的量子势能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:10:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有可能影响到在其中心的小遥的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遥 可能会成为博士你的理论的实例
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子化的不确定的世界被确定的现象的产生\N是由于人类所擅长的量子构造
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「确定一切人的存在 人是时空重迭而产生的\N是宇宙的根源 是网络的中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是博士的理论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这一切都可能会因为Magic Circle计划而崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大人是不能破坏孩子们的未来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是上乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓也先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 我稍微出去一下 拜托你看家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去买东西了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨没有发现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想还没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要祈祷吗 来祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥被转移到了香格里拉的根据是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有存在反应 但是无法特定的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅是那个存在也在不安定化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转移到时空大量非灵子化的香格里拉去了 是最妥当的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个香格里拉是指哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢 用龙之转矩的数据进行逆算固定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做的话 就能确定香格里拉的位置了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香格里拉是很不安定的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥有消失的危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做实验也是没有办法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢啊 把我送到香格里拉去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有人都解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说让你把我送到香格里拉去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么粗鲁的说话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢 传送我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乱来了 能不能正确的转移到香格里拉的可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我 你做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 那家伙又…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向井
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了啊 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.33,0:12:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对我生气 现在生气的是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样粗暴下去 真的真的不原谅你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也不和你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连公园也…哪里都不带你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不闭嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭啦 很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么好点的方法了吗 鸢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不快点对香格里拉做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙所在的世界也会被吞噬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想守护这些家伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我可以问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为大人以后是不是全都是痛苦的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能什么都不知道的小孩子的时候要快乐的多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子的时候也有痛苦的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为大人以后小时侯的记忆就渐渐淡忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又没关系 即使忘记了小时侯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不自由 没有什么快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为大人以后并不代表就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满了孩提时代所无法想象的痛苦和艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你要变强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拥有即使遇到了许许多多悲伤痛苦的事 也能够超越它的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的遥 死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 河童君们还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想要拜托一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸢 郡山先生在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郡山先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然把你叫出来实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之前你们不是才见面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在东京呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想和你商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和遥到东京来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住的地方已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个城市将实行一个实验 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样危险的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能说 但请你明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着遥立刻去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是和以前一样啊 总是认为自己是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的实验 到其它地方好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是我出生的城市啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是和以前一样啊 都不好好听对方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要谈的只有这些的话 我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 你等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是遥的母亲不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好考虑一下女儿的事怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你说那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又吵了呢 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就冲动起来是我的坏习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我取消刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变的温和了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有义务保护你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 下次见面的时候 和遥一起三人再到那个公园去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再联络你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所在的时空的遥变成了量子计算机的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在你们的时间轴的10年后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么遥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥自身是那么期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让拉库利玛存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献上了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防止时空间的侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥被选中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为了防止不同时空侵蚀的城墙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了量子计算机制造出的 隔开时空的墙壁——Limes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Limes:拉丁语“防线” 意为阻隔自我理性与本能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救拉库利玛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥成为了一座桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我…对遥见死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉库利玛的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉库利玛的我也喜欢鸦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有时空的遥都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾们消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是和鸦、佑没有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你期望的 我就不对他们出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起把所有的时空变成一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次孕育正确的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 你的存在可以拯救所有的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑和鸦也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我约定将佑和鸦送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是你的期望的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了正确的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了的 快点把两人送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙的事还是忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.38,0:21:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点察觉到吧 遥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界是不幸的连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那个连锁的开始…就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田小姐他们能不能找到什么好的方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀 鸢还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:21:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.43,0:22:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:22:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…家？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.57,0:24:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏日的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.60,0:24:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能够明白未来是不幸的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.25,0:24:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让他们回去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.60,0:25:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.57,0:25:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.29,0:25:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 向未来而去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.01,0:25:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找到幸福的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:33.44,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}眠れない夜　秒針の音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:39.71,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}冷蔵庫が虚空に唸る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:45.54,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}ブラインド越しの月が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.55,0:23:49.44,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}満ち欠けるようにいつかは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:55.29,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}痛みは温もりに変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:24:06.29,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}時の舟　どこへ流されても
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.46,0:24:10.63,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}めぐり逢えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.66,0:24:16.14,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}傷痕から夜明けの足音
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.24,0:24:19.40,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}溜め息より密かに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.42,0:24:25.54,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}新しい毎日が降りそそぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.54,0:24:31.07,ed_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}どんな空にも
